    <metadata>
        <name>Flatts Lane - Eston Hills Actual</name>
        <desc>8.2 miles.
1025 feet ascent measured on Komoot.
Walk Grade = Moderate
John's walk.
Route 186.
8 July 2026.
Park at Flatts Lane Woodland Country Park.  It is free.
No seats. Can sit on walls at the "castle" at the eastern end of the walk.
Royal Observer Corps (ROC) Monitoring Post. Built in 1963 and closed in 1968.  Designed to survive a nuclear attack and measure radioactive fallout. (OS Grid Ref NZ 5583 1769).</desc>
        <bounds minlat="54.5374200" minlon="-1.1596000" maxlat="54.5622300" maxlon="-1.1060900"/>
